"Specifies whether to log class VI calls to the NI Spy utility.  If spying is enabled, you can use NI Spy to view the input and output parameters, return values, coercion records, and interchangeability warnings of class VI calls.
    The default value is TRUE.
    
TRUE 1
True

FALSE 0
False"
